w the road surface. (ce2aed65 6aef 4c6f ba46 2ba44f5","desc":"A worker on the North Parkway. Crews working below the road surface.","credit":"NPS · Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Crews_working_below_the_road_surface._(ce2aed65-6aef-4c6f-ba46-2ba44f57c3f7).png"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/ab/Crews_pave_new_asphalt_on_the_GWMP._%28d931168b-a8d1-44c2-8291-96a90253f009%29.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/ab/Crews_pave_new_asphalt_on_the_GWMP._%28d931168b-a8d1-44c2-8291-96a90253f009%29.jpg","cap":"Crews pave new asphalt on the GWMP. (d931168b a8d1 44c2 8291 96a90253f","desc":"A man driving a steam roller. Crews pave new asphalt on the GWMP.","credit":"NPS · Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Crews_pave_new_asphalt_on_the_GWMP._(d931168b-a8d1-44c2-8291-96a90253f009).jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/77/Fort_Hunt_Area_A_Pavilion_%283587d3e9-1dd8-b71c-07b2-352a7b1f1c28%29.jpg/1280px-Fort_Hunt_Area_A_Pavilion_%283587d3e9-1dd8-b71c-07b2-352a7b1f1c28%29.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/77/Fort_Hunt_Area_A_Pavilion_%283587d3e9-1dd8-b71c-07b2-352a7b1f1c28%29.jpg","cap":"Fort Hunt Area A Pavilion (3587d3e9 1dd8 b71c 07b2 352a7b1f1c28)","desc":"Large wooden picnic pavilion with paved loading zone Area A can accommodate up to 600 people and 150 cars. It has a paved loading zone; a pavilion with a stage, electricity, fireplace, ADA-compliant restrooms; approximately 75 picnic tables (including one ADA-compliant table); and volleyball pits.","credit":"NPS · Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Fort_Hunt_Area_A_Pavilion_(3587d3e9-1dd8-b71c-07b2-352a7b1f1c28).jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bb/Fort_Hunt_Area_B_Pavilion_%28358e83f3-1dd8-b71c-0761-2a4bf5bbc69a%29.jpg/1280px-Fort_Hunt_Area_B_Pavilion_%28358e83f3-1dd8-b71c-0761-2a4bf5bbc69a%29.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/bb/Fort_Hunt_Area_B_Pavilion_%28358e83f3-1dd8-b71c-0761-2a4bf5bbc69a%29.jpg","cap":"Fort Hunt Area B Pavilion (358e83f3 1dd8 b71c 0761 2a4bf5bbc69a)","desc":"Wooden picnic pavilion Area B can accommodate up to 350 people and 140 cars. It has a pavilion, restrooms, approximately 44 picnic tables (including one ADA-compliant table), and a softball field. There is no loading zone.","credit":"NPS · Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Fort_Hunt_Area_B_Pavilion_(358e83f3-1dd8-b71c-0761-2a4bf5bbc69a).jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/33/Fort_Hunt_Area_C-1_%2835960630-1dd8-b71c-0708-3f81ec2bae71%29.jpg/1280px-Fort_Hunt_Area_C-1_%2835960630-1dd8-b71c-0708-3f81ec2bae71%29.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/33/Fort_Hunt_Area_C-1_%2835960630-1dd8-b71c-0708-3f81ec2bae71%29.jpg","cap":"Fort Hunt Area C 1 (35960630 1dd8 b71c 0708 3f81ec2bae71)","desc":"Cluster of picnic tables under trees Area C-1 can accommodate up to 100 people and 40 cars. It has a gravel loading zone and approximately 13 picnic tables. There is no pavilion on site.","credit":"NPS · Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Fort_Hunt_Area_C-1_(35960630-1dd8-b71c-0708-3f81ec2bae71).jpg"},{"url":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cd/Fort_Hunt_Area_C-2_Pavilion_%28359dfe01-1dd8-b71c-0722-dab7703c23a6%29.jpg/1280px-Fort_Hunt_Area_C-2_Pavilion_%28359dfe01-1dd8-b71c-0722-dab7703c23a6%29.jpg","full":"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/c/cd/Fort_Hunt_Area_C-2_Pavilion_%28359dfe01-1dd8-b71c-0722-dab7703c23a6%29.jpg","cap":"Fort Hunt Area C 2 Pavilion (359dfe01 1dd8 b71c 0722 dab7703c23a6)","desc":"Wooden picnic pavilion Area C-2 can accommodate up to 120 people and 40 cars. It has a gravel loading zone, a pavilion, and approximately 15 picnic tables (including one ADA-compliant table).","credit":"NPS · Public domain","pageUrl":"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Fort_Hunt_Area_C-2_Pavilion_(359dfe01-1dd8-b71c-0722-dab7703c23a6).jpg"}]}